snippet.title: Chicken Run | Official Game Interview | Netflix
snippet.description:
Get ready for egg-citing gameplay with CHICKEN RUN: EGGSTRACTION - the top-down stealth action game by the creators of Chicken Run. Dive behind the scenes with Aardman Studios in our Dev Diary BTS. Coming soon, exclusively on mobile with Netflix. #GeekedWeek

SUBSCRIBE: http://bit.ly/29qBUt7

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services with over 247 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Chicken Run | Official Game Interview | Netflix
